title: 286 - Doin' the Doobie
description:
Do you realize that the little successes in life matter? A lot of us chase the “Touchdown Moments” in life but fail to recognize that the small wins leading to the big moments are just as valuable, if not more. In this episode, the guys use Football as an analogy of how to maximize your success in life.
